<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/fonts.css">
  <title>Refund Policy</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800" style="font-family:'Open Sans', sans-serif;">
  <%- include('partials/userNavbar', { navbarTheme: 'light' }) %>

  <section class="pt-28 pb-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-700 text-white p-8 sm:p-10 shadow-xl mb-8">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gray-300">Camverse Policies</p>
        <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold mt-2">Refund Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-300 font-extralight">
          This page explains how refunds are processed for cancellations and returns.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">1. Eligibility</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight">
            Refunds are applicable for eligible cancelled orders and approved return requests.
            Products must satisfy the return conditions shown at the time of order.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">2. Refund Method</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight">
            Refunds are credited to your Camverse wallet. You can track all wallet credits and debits
            in the Wallet section of your account.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">3. Coupon Impact on Refunds</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight">
            If a coupon was applied and a partial cancellation/return makes the remaining order amount
            ineligible for that coupon, refund may be adjusted by coupon deduction as per order rules.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">4. Processing Time</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight">
            Wallet refunds are usually reflected shortly after cancellation or return approval.
            In exceptional cases, processing can take longer.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">5. Contact Support</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base font-extralight">
            If you have questions regarding a refund, contact support from your account order details.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/userFooter') %>
  <script src="/js/user/homePage.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
